<PageLayout title="About">
    <h1>Our Mission</h1>
    <p>The vision of the Benicia Middle School PTO is to promote a community where:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Parents are informed and involved</li>
        <li>Teachers are empowered to deliver the richest education possible</li>
        <li>Children have access to resources that keep them engaged, stimulated and excited to learn</li>
        <li>The PTO will aim to ensure that every student is known, valued and nurtured in order to reach their fullest academic and social-emotional potential</li>
        <li>Membership is open to all parents and teachers at BMS and there is no membership fee</li>
        <li>We are an independent non-profit and not politically connected to any outside organization</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We can focus all of our funds and attention on the unique needs of our school community!</p>

    <p>If you have any questions, please reach out to us at <a href="mailto:bmsptoinfo@googlegroups.com">bmsptoinfo@googlegroups.com</a>.</p>

